title: Not easy to come out of Ms Dhoni's shadow: Wriddhiman Saha
text:
*New Delhi:* Mahendra Singh Dhoni's boots are too big to fill in and no one knows it more than Wriddhiman Saha, who put himself several notches below India's One-day skipper in an honest evaluation.
*Wriddhiman Saha*
